  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Quadrilaterals <math alttext=\"upper P upper Q upper R upper S\"><mi>P</mi><mi>Q</mi><mi>R</mi><mi>S</mi></math> and <math alttext=\"upper W upper X upper Y upper Z\"><mi>W</mi><mi>X</mi><mi>Y</mi><mi>Z</mi></math> are similar, where <math alttext=\"upper P\"><mi>P</mi>\n</math>, <math alttext=\"upper Q\"><mi>Q</mi>\n</math>, and <math alttext=\"upper R\"><mi>R</mi>\n</math> correspond to <math alttext=\"upper W\"><mi>W</mi>\n</math>, <math alttext=\"upper X\"><mi>X</mi>\n</math>, and <math alttext=\"upper Y\"><mi>Y</mi>\n</math>, respectively. The measure of&nbsp;<math alttext=\"angle upper S\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>S</mi></math> is <math alttext=\"135 degree\"><mn>135</mn>\n<mo>&#176;</mo></math>, <math alttext=\"upper P upper S equals 45\"><mrow>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<mi>P</mi>\n\t\t<mi>S</mi>\n\t</mrow>\n\t<mo>=</mo>\n\t<mn>45</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math>, and <math alttext=\"upper W upper Z equals 9\"><mrow>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<mi>W</mi>\n\t\t<mi>Z</mi>\n\t</mrow>\n\t<mo>=</mo>\n\t<mn>9</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math>. What is the measure of <math alttext=\"angle upper Z\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>Z</mi></math>?</p>",
