  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. Corresponding angles in similar figures have equal measure.&nbsp;It's given that quadrilaterals <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"upper P upper Q upper R upper S\"><mi>P</mi><mi>Q</mi><mi>R</mi><mi>S</mi></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"upper W upper X upper Y upper Z\"><mi>W</mi><mi>X</mi><mi>Y</mi><mi>Z</mi></math> are similar and that <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"upper P\"><mi>P</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"upper Q\"><mi>Q</mi></math>, and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"upper R\"><mi>R</mi></math> correspond to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"upper W\"><mi>W</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"upper X\"><mi>X</mi></math>, and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"upper Y\"><mi>Y</mi></math>. It follows that <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"angle upper S\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>S</mi></math> corresponds to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"angle upper Z\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>Z</mi></math>. It's also given that the measure of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"angle upper S\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>S</mi></math> is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"135 degree\"><mn>135</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math>. Therefore, the measure of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"angle upper Z\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>Z</mi></math> is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"135 degree\"><mn>135</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math>.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Choice A is incorrect and may result from conceptual errors.</p>\n<p>Choice B is incorrect and may result from conceptual errors.</p>\n<p>Choice C is incorrect. This is the supplement of the measure of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"angle upper Z\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>Z</mi></math>, not the measure of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"angle upper Z\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>Z</mi></math>.</p>",
